d.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c1/Joker_2019_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc1%2FJoker_2019_poster.jpg&h=7f26b03e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/The_Rundown_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2FThe_Rundown_poster.jpg&h=1b49fd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.魯本&middot;迪什科夫（艾略特&middot;高德飾）患心肌梗塞後，丹尼爾&middot;奧申（喬治&middot;克隆尼飾）等十人圍在他的病床前。四星期前，拉斯維加斯賭場大亨威利&middot;班克（艾爾&middot;帕西諾飾）與魯本在二人合資的新賭場工地中見面。魯本為班克爭取到了關鍵的合同後，班克使出老手段，迫使他交出股份。過度的驚嚇使魯本犯了心臟病。<br />\n奧申等人發誓要為魯本復仇，要在班克的酒店正式開業當晚使其破產。為了達到這個目標，所有的賭客都必須贏錢。由於資金不足，班克在新酒店的建設過程中不得不向一些競爭對手尋求幫助.....<br />\n<br />\n2.1981年，中年男子亞瑟&middot;佛萊克因工作需要扮演成小丑。亞瑟與他的母親潘妮&middot;佛萊克一同居住在高譚市。高譚市正因為垃圾堆積、失業、犯罪和經濟蕭條而沉陷，使部分人民陷入貧窮以及失去基本權利。亞瑟患有神經系統疾病，導致他在不合時宜的時候大笑，須接受社福機構人員的治療以獲取藥物。一次工作中，一群小孩在巷弄裡毆打他，之後亞瑟的同事藍道借給他槍枝，希望他被欺負時能自保。回到家搭電梯時，亞瑟遇到鄰居單身媽媽蘇菲&middot;杜蒙，與她有了一小段交流，並邀請她改天觀看他的單口喜劇表演，然後他們開始交往。 <br />\n<br />\n3.賞金獵人貝克（巨石強森）為他的僱主比利去巴西熱帶雨林尋找叛逆離家的兒子特拉維斯（西恩&middot;威廉&middot;史考特），貝克租用了戴克林的飛機和汽車來到巴西熱帶雨林，卻發現康奈紐斯&middot;伯納德&middot;哈奇（克里斯多夫&middot;華肯）非法奴役當地的印第安人為他挖礦淘金。特拉維斯曾經在美國史丹福大學讀書，中途輟學來到這裡尋找印第安文化中遺失的寶物「嘎圖」（一尊神像），他和印地安女孩瑪麗&middot;安娜（羅莎里奧&middot;道森）是好友，兩人都對嘎圖有著強烈的好奇心，兩人都懂葡萄牙語。貝克捉到了特拉維斯之後，激怒了殖民主哈奇，哈奇派遣一支隊伍將對他們窮追不捨，二人在逃亡中遇到了當地印第安人<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=bd41812d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=0b78fb90\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1c15095cc37ba74e8c914e8b4d0b954b4f5831","tid":1703715,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5299f95b321e756e80775dce8460b16097f28a5","tid":1703715,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f179458da287509f859c5ba0a7c2bf3e4499870","tid":1703715,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5673e377ba521cff647445b3fa6eb9b987fca43c","tid":1703715,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6ea933595d0f9055d3c433ee766458ec85e396","tid":1703715,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31476b387806fe2997f73641aa51792d1907a23e","tid":1703715,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe